block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This is Paper plane 22 of our 100 Exotic Paper Airplane Challenge. Avion F-5 by Carlos Pomaron. This is an origami plane folded from a square sheet. If you missed my last Exotic Paper Airplane "Paper Plane 021 : Simple Dart by John Smith ", you could watch it at https://youtu.be/t3fGWVhPeQk Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
